elements.name: errorMessage
elements.textContent: Your request to delete your account cannot be completed because of one of the following reasons: • You have a screening scheduled or pending • You have received or accepted an offer • You are currently on-boarded to a project • You are in the process of off-boarding from a project Please excuse yourself from any active roles on the Talent Exchange or complete the off-boarding process before deleting your account.
